Class TestExactRecovery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ericbarnhill.jmra.TestExactRecovery

  • public class TestExactRecovery
extends Object
    Tests exact recovery of data after wavelet decomposition and recomposition. Note that 3D decimated wavelet also produces some error in the "gold standard" built-in Matlab implementation. The other transforms should all produce error of < 1e-5 .
